%N A173848 Number of permutations of 1..n with no adjacent pair summing to n + 8.
%C A173848 If a(n,k) is the number of permutations of 1..n with no adjacent pair summing to n+k, then a(n,k) = a(n,k+1) for n+k even.
%F A173848 k = 8; m = max(0, floor((n-k+1)/2)); a(n,k) = Sum_{j=0..m} (-2)^j * binomial(m,j)*(n-j)!.
